      "writtenOn": "2020-09-23T23:32:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I actually use the ContentHash returned from LUCI Config. I\u0027m digging into details to see how it is computed. I was actually debating between using the ContentHash from LUCI Config and hashing by ourselves before. I picked the former for simplicity, but the latter one will gave us more control and not coupling it from implementation in LUCI Config. WDYT?\n\n[1]: https://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/config/interface.go;l\u003d36-37;drc\u003d1fac7eaf1ca957f249547201ce2819253e050a67",
