      "writtenOn": "2020-11-07T00:58:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "let\u0027s hash ourselves, as LUCI Config may change in the future.\nAlso, let\u0027s prefix the kind of hash into the resulting string. Costs only 5 bytes, but makes migration trivial:\n\n  sha2:\u003chash\u003e[:16]\n\ne.g. \n  sha2:deadbeefbdeadbeef\n\n(8 bytes (aka 16 chars) of entropy suffices)",
